- **News portal PRD (table list):** [documentation/news_portal/backend_prd.html](mdc:documentation/news_portal/backend_prd.html) and [documentation/news_portal/generic_prd.html](mdc:documentation/news_portal/generic_prd.html)

## **Summary Checklist for New Tables**

- [ ] `id bigint DEFAULT nextval('public.sequence_generator'::regclass) NOT NULL` and `PRIMARY KEY (id)`
- [ ] `tenant_id character varying(255)` (if tenant-scoped)
- [ ] `created_at` and `updated_at` with `DEFAULT now() NOT NULL` where applicable
- [ ] DROP TABLE added at top in reverse dependency order
- [ ] CREATE TABLE added in dependency order (parents before children)
- [ ] Table added to `sequence_generator` setval GREATEST list
- [ ] No stale hardcoded `sequence_generator` value left without `MAX(id)` protection for newly-added tables
- [ ] No ALTER used; only CREATE TABLE for new tables
